java.lang.Object

      com.netflix.msl.io.LZWInputStream
All Implemented Interfaces:
Closeable
public class LZWInputStream
extends InputStream

This class implements a stream filter for reading compressed data in the LZW format.

decompress

private int decompress(byte[] b,
                       int off,
                       int len)
                throws IOException
Reads compressed data from the underlying input stream and decompresses the codes to the original data.

Parameters:
b - the buffer into which the data is read.
off - the start offset in array b at which the data is written.
len - the maximum number of bytes to read.
Returns:
the number of bytes decoded into the buffer.
Throws:
IOException - if there is an error reading from the code stream.
